### Health check
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### ATHLETES
### ===========================================

### Create Participant - Athlete (Swimming, USA)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Katie",
  "familyName": "Ledecky",
  "gender": "F",
  "birthDate": "1997-03-17",
  "organisation": "USA",
  "functions": [
    {
      "function": "ATH",
      "discipline": "SWM",
      "isMain": true
    }
  ]
}

