### ===========================================
### QUERIES
### ===========================================

### Get Participant by ID (replace with actual LOC- id from create response)
GET {{host}}/api/participants/LOC-replace-with-actual-id
Accept: application/json

### Get Participant (not found)
GET {{host}}/api/participants/9999999
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by Organisation - USA
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-organisation/USA
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by Organisation - Costa Rica
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-organisation/CRC
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by Organisation - Spain
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-organisation/ESP
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### LOCALIZED RESPONSES
### ===========================================

### Get Participant in Spanish
GET {{host}}/api/participants/LOC-replace-with-actual-id
Accept: application/json
Language: spa

### Get Participant in Portuguese
GET {{host}}/api/participants/LOC-replace-with-actual-id
Accept: application/json
Language: por

### ===========================================
### VALIDATION ERRORS
### ===========================================

### Validation: empty functions
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "gender": "M",
  "organisation": "USA",
  "functions": []
}

### Validation: function without functionId
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "gender": "M",
  "organisation": "USA",
  "functions": [
    {
      "function": "",
      "discipline": "SWM",
      "isMain": true
    }
  ]
}

### Validation: invalid organisation (not in CommonCodes)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "gender": "M",
  "organisation": "ZZZ",
  "functions": [
    {
      "function": "ATH",
      "discipline": "SWM",
      "isMain": true
    }
  ]
}

### Validation: invalid function code (not in CommonCodes)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "gender": "M",
  "organisation": "USA",
  "functions": [
    {
      "function": "INVALID_FN",
      "discipline": "SWM",
      "isMain": true
    }
  ]
}

### Validation: invalid discipline code (not in CommonCodes)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
